transbit.tbits.common.readerizer
Class Readerizer

java.lang.Object
  transbit.tbits.common.readerizer.Readerizer

public class Readerizer
extends java.lang.Object

This class extracts text from different types of files. It employs special text extractors for the following types of files:

  • PDF -> PDFBox
  • DOC -> Antiword
  • RTF -> Java Swing's RTFEditorKit
  • XLS -> xls2csv
  • XLT -> xls2csv
  • XLA -> xls2csv
  • WKS -> xls2csv
  • PPT -> Apache POI's PowerpointExtractor
  • PPS -> Apache POI's PowerpointExtractor
The following types of files are considered as text files during extraction:
  • asp
  • bas
  • csv
  • java
  • js
  • jsp
  • log
  • msg
  • pl
  • pm
  • properties
  • sql
  • txt
  • xml
  • rsl
  • xsl
